= SDL_GetRendererInfo =
Use this function to get information about the current rendering context.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_GetRendererInfo(SDL_RendererInfo* info)
```

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''info'''
|an [[SDL_RendererInfo]] structure filled with information about the current renderer
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success or a negative error code on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

